Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started,\Nyou can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, there's lots of Sonoko\Nin her natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Danger, romance and fate await!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:46.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Izu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking a picture of your butt while\Nyou were fixing your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real close-up!\NIt's an eyeful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nwith a photo like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna show it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nwhen he gets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think how happy he'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi wouldn't be\Nhappy about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nso too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does a little kid know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:34.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh... I can't {\i1}wait{\i0} to\Nget back to normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been acting weird, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been picking on me\Nnon-stop for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.\NI'm just a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?\NDid I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd we come on a weekend\Nbeach trip to Izu in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you, it's your usual\Nman-hunting trip, isn't it, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's a carefully planned\Npoor girl vacation, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always stay at my family's\Nsummer house, or an expensive hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh, {\i1}how{\i0} can I talk to a girl\Nwho's so far beyond my reach?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, we're staying at an old inn,\Nwhere we can reel in unexpecting boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the train here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the fireworks show last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even at this beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the guys are after you.\NEvery single one of them, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} a photo of you\Nin your underwear that I took last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\NI'll never forgive you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.\NNever took any photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, she was bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tadahiko Michiwaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to get some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! We'd love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want {\i1}her{\i0}, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take her! She's in season!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't try anything funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I was kinda hoping to\Nget to know {\i1}you{\i0} better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did it, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Impossible. This is Sonoko\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:58.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There has to be\Nsomething behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've {\i1}got{\i0} to stop thinking\Nlike a detective all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I\Nwill stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:20.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nagisa Beach House\NFamous for our Grilled Amberjack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a student at Beika\NUniversity, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's dad used to\Nstudy there, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She gets all excited about a guy,\Nbut she wimps out and drags us along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwhat brings you to Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a trip\Nto heal a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was gazing into\Nthe sea in despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...when an angel\Nappeared before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a hunch you're the\Ngoddess who's going to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your draft beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:17.69,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sir, please don't drop cigarette\Nbutts all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,They're a pain to clean up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a rude waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we seen that\Nwaiter somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we have. His dad owns\Nthe inn where we're staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's come to help\Nover summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was staring at us from the front steps\Nof the inn, so I asked one of the workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why's he working {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably run by the same person who takes\Ncare of Kawaraya Inn, where we're staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're staying at Kawaraya Inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fancy that, it's right next to my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about we all have dinner at\Na fancy restaurant by the sea tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't forget to\Nbring your camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just learned this from a local,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was an incident at\Nthe beach near the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a girl with long brown hair was stabbed\Nrepeatedly in the stomach and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was killed on her\Nway to that restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there were no witnesses.\NThe police are still looking for the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so most people forgot about it,\Nand the restaurant's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, she seems to have taken a\Nliking to that restaurant, and still drops by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:07:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victimized woman shows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as a grotesque ghost in photos taken inside the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's see if she really\Nappears in a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have about ten\Nshots left in my camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't even bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we showed it to Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nhe might notice something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're going to show him\Nthe {\i1}shocking{\i0} photo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point of showing him that one?\NYou can't even tell who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could figure it out with\Nhis super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deductive skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her boyfriend's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's in that photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of customers waiting,\Nso hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with that waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he have a grudge\Nagainst us or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.90,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shoji Terabayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't we eat somewhere\Nother than that restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost thing's just a rumor,\Nand it's been a year since the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the dead woman got\Nbored of that restaurant by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found another one in\Nthe forest by the train tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bloody body of a\Nwoman with brown hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what a bundle of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:12.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo\NShizuoka Police Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Stabbed multiple times\Nin the abdominal area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just like a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman seems to\Nhave been a tourist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's the\Nestimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between 8 and 9 PM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was right after the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that around\Nthe time we passed by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at me!\NI have brown hair too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee\NI won't be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with my whole\Nlife ahead of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you as long\Nas you're here in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess we should change\Nour dinner reservations, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up around 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in front of the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wasn't that guy just at\Nthe Beach House, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI'll be looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go back\Nto change clothes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've come to Izu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we came for the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is the great\NDetective Mouri here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're the knight accompanying\Nthese two damsels, huh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nwe've had a troubling incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give Detective Mouri my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's as cheerful\Nas always, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's not\Nhaving any luck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your dad was here,\Nhe'd solve the case in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:37.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Detective Yokomizo is {\i1}far{\i0} more\Ncompetent than the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's starting to rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nshows up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hero always appears\Nat the last second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he wants us to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's got a crush\Non you, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting popular, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the dark guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you already\Nhave Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ran,\Nyou're making me blush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, drat.\NI left my purse in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on,\NI'll be back in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} I've seen the guy\Nin glasses somewhere, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in this inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where'd you\Nsee him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko? What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A weird guy jumped me...\NHe escaped through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn! He got away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I opened the door,\Nhe was searching our bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to shout,\Nand he grabbed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Searching our bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he was trying to\Nsteal our underwear! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?\NYou saw his face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never had the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pitch dark in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so scared,\NI just about passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how do you know it's a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bit his arm in the struggle.\NIt was hairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the lights out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car broke down on the way here,\Nso I ran here as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please accept my\Napologies for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how'd you find our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find you two outside,\Nso I asked one of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:18.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His shirt's wet\Nand his pants are muddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:18.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind\Ntaking your shirt off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could\Nshow me your upper arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nwrong with my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nothing. No tooth\Nmarks from Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy now, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your right arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is from a little struggle I had with a drunk customer earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was that? Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was him.\NThe guy who attacked me was hairier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A man came in through this\Nwindow, dug through our bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and attacked Sonoko when she\Nhappened to walk in on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he ran off as soon\Nas he heard us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must've been a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've had this happen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did? Then why\Ndidn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} tell you to make\Nsure to lock up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walking around in a midriff top at this\Ntime of night, what are you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're practically {\i1}asking{\i0}\Nto be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even look\Ngood on you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite top, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You look\Ngood in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move you.\NThere's another room open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to spend the night\Nin the room where you were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd also advise you not to go out,\Nand have dinner here at the inn instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never know if that man\Nmight be waiting for you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food's much better than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we'd known this before,\Nwe would've eaten here last night, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would've been able to get you a nicer meal\Nif you'd made reservations in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the meal's on the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...if you don't spread any "rumors"\Nabout a thief lurking around the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't talk about the inn with an\Nunderwear thief who pulled a knife on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught a glimpse of it shining in the light coming through the side screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a sharp, gleaming knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:23.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if our thief is the same man who\Nkilled the woman found in the woods today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:30.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Supposedly a year ago, here in Izu,\Na brown-haired woman was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:36.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why would the\Nkiller target Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just because she has brown hair?\NThat's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:46.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The guy who attacked Sonoko\Nransacked her belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:52.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's one thing in her luggage that\Ncould be connected to the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:58.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe one of the photos captured\Nsomething related to the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Did the guy who\Nattacked you steal your camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the compartment\Nwhere I had it {\i1}was{\i0} open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he stole the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I finished off\Nall thirty-six photos,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we could all\Nlook at them over dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I had them developed\Nthis afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?\NI've got the photos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept that special photo\Nof you for safe-keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know all of these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have interrupted\Na lot of lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko was all cranky\Nbefore she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She kept pranking\Nall the couples we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange... There's nothing\Nodd about the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't see the victim, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:01.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We {\i1}did{\i0} pass through the forest\Nwhere the body was found last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but Sonoko didn't\Ntake any photos then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:12.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So what made the killer think\NSonoko'd taken an incriminating photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:22.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe someone overheard her at lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:27.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He could figure it out with\Nhis super deductive skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:32.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nagisa Beach House\NFamous for our Grilled Amberjack
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer could've been in\Nthe Beach House at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But was it really {\i1}that{\i0}\Nsuspicious a remark?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're going home\Ntomorrow at noon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how about we stop by the\Ncursed restaurant in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be as scary\Nin the daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Am I imagining things,\Nor does this guy keep watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:06.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what about that guy in the glasses,\Nthe one Ran thinks she's seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And as for the guy\Nwho attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was he really just a simple thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hand brake's disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, wake up! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:09.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!\NSonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:15.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Toothmarks
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:21.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Finally Sonoko's got herself a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:23.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:25.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This won't end with just being happy!
